19
00:00:18,606 --> 00:00:20,775
<i>Ahsoka Tano captured!</i>

20
00:00:20,942 --> 00:00:23,778
<i>While on the run to prove her innocence,</i>

21
00:00:23,945 --> 00:00:26,030
<i>Padawan Tano teamed up
with the deadly Asajj Ventress</i>

22
00:00:26,113 --> 00:00:29,784
<i>to find the rogue Jedi
who framed Ahsoka for murder.</i>

23
00:00:30,451 --> 00:00:34,163
<i>The Jedi Council sent
Anakin Skywalker and Master Plo Koon</i>

24
00:00:34,288 --> 00:00:37,792
<i>to track Ahsoka down
and bring her back to the Temple.</i>

25
00:00:37,959 --> 00:00:41,254
<i>Now, captured and imprisoned,
Ahsoka faces punishment</i>

26
00:00:41,587 --> 00:00:43,965
<i>for crimes she did not commit.</i>

27
00:00:44,674 --> 00:00:48,261
<i>The Senate requests that Ahsoka Tano
be indicted for acts of treason</i>

28
00:00:48,427 --> 00:00:49,971
<i>against the Republic.</i>

29
00:00:50,263 --> 00:00:52,932
A fair trial Padawan Tano will have,

30
00:00:53,307 --> 00:00:55,351
in accordance with Jedi tradition.

31
00:00:55,768 --> 00:00:58,020
<i>Ah, yes, Jedi tradition.</i>

32
00:00:58,479 --> 00:01:03,401
<i>I'm afraid, Master Yoda, that the Senate
believes that an internal Jedi trial</i>

33
00:01:03,484 --> 00:01:05,319
<i>would seem biased.</i>

34
00:01:05,403 --> 00:01:07,488
<i>Therefore, the Senate asks</i>

35
00:01:07,572 --> 00:01:11,158
<i>that the Council expel Ahsoka Tano
from the Jedi Order</i>

36
00:01:11,284 --> 00:01:13,828
<i>so that she may be put
to a Republic military tribunal,</i>

37
00:01:14,287 --> 00:01:17,164
<i>where she will receive
more impartial judgment.</i>

38
00:01:17,498 --> 00:01:21,961
And who would represent Ahsoka
in this tribunal, Admiral?

39
00:01:22,295 --> 00:01:24,839
<i>That would be up to the Council, General,</i>

40
00:01:24,964 --> 00:01:27,842
<i>but I would recommend
someone outside the Order.</i>

41
00:01:28,175 --> 00:01:29,594
Of course.

42
00:01:29,677 --> 00:01:32,513
The Council will act
as they deem necessary.

43
00:01:33,347 --> 00:01:34,765
Thank you, Admiral.

44
00:01:36,851 --> 00:01:40,021
Surely, we cannot do
what Tarkin suggests.

45
00:01:40,187 --> 00:01:42,189
We need to stand together with Ahsoka.

46
00:01:42,356 --> 00:01:44,734
And yet there's evidence that she is indeed

47
00:01:44,817 --> 00:01:47,361
the mastermind
behind the attack on the Temple.

48
00:01:47,987 --> 00:01:52,199
She was found in possession
of nano-droid explosives.

49
00:01:52,325 --> 00:01:54,327
This alone is enough to convict her.

50
00:01:54,493 --> 00:01:57,163
I understand your sentiment, Obi-Wan,

51
00:01:57,413 --> 00:02:00,041
but, if the Council does as you suggest,

52
00:02:00,124 --> 00:02:03,377
it could be seen as an act
of opposition to the Senate.

53
00:02:03,753 --> 00:02:05,838
I'm afraid we have little choice.

54
00:02:08,799 --> 00:02:13,012
To the Chamber of Judgment,
summon Skywalker and his Padawan.

55
00:02:13,262 --> 00:02:16,849
And, in our decision,
may the Force guide us.

56
00:02:31,197 --> 00:02:32,948
You're not helping.

57
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:36,702
I'm sorry, Snips, I just...

58
00:02:37,203 --> 00:02:38,788
I just don't know what to do.

59
00:02:38,871 --> 00:02:39,914
It's okay.

60
00:02:40,414 --> 00:02:41,916
I don't, either.

61
00:03:20,454 --> 00:03:24,959
Padawan Tano, serious charges
have been levied against you.

62
00:03:25,126 --> 00:03:26,836
How plead you?

63
00:03:26,961 --> 00:03:31,424
Not guilty, Master.
I would never take the lives of innocents.

64
00:03:31,465 --> 00:03:34,301
The values of the Jedi are sacred to me.

65
00:03:34,468 --> 00:03:36,429
There is evidence to the contrary.

66
00:03:36,470 --> 00:03:39,932
You were alone with Letta Turmond
when she died. Can you explain this?

67
00:03:40,808 --> 00:03:43,477
Someone used the Force against her.

68
00:03:43,644 --> 00:03:47,773
Which brings us to Ventress.
Can you explain your association with her?

69
00:03:47,982 --> 00:03:51,694
We had a mutual understanding.
I thought she was helping me.

70
00:03:51,819 --> 00:03:52,862
Did she help you acquire

71
00:03:52,987 --> 00:03:55,698
the nano-droid weapons we found on you
when you were apprehended,

72
00:03:55,823 --> 00:03:57,700
the same devices used in the bombing
of the Temple?

73
00:03:57,992 --> 00:03:59,285
No!

74
00:03:59,326 --> 00:04:03,497
I was set up and deceived,
as you are being deceived now.

75
00:04:04,081 --> 00:04:07,793
The question is, Padawan Tano,
who is deceiving us,

76
00:04:07,835 --> 00:04:10,337
Ventress, you, or someone else?

77
00:04:10,504 --> 00:04:12,423
I am not deceiving you!

78
00:04:12,506 --> 00:04:16,135
I would assume Ventress is,
but I can't be sure.

79
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:19,013
My sense is clouded.

80
00:04:19,138 --> 00:04:23,184
Clouded by the dark side
these things are, Padawan Tano.

81
00:04:23,267 --> 00:04:24,852
Dangerously clouded.

82
00:04:25,144 --> 00:04:26,854
But not just surrounding you,

83
00:04:26,979 --> 00:04:30,024
surrounding many things, in these times.

84
00:04:30,191 --> 00:04:32,526
You've already made your decision,
haven't you?

85
00:04:32,610 --> 00:04:34,695
This meeting is just a formality!

86
00:04:37,031 --> 00:04:41,660
Reached a decision we have,
though not in total agreement are we.

87
00:04:42,369 --> 00:04:44,538
It is the Council's opinion

88
00:04:44,705 --> 00:04:48,209
that Padawan Ahsoka Tano has committed
sedition against the Republic,

89
00:04:48,375 --> 00:04:52,129
and thus she will be expelled
from the Jedi Order.

90
00:04:53,881 --> 00:04:55,174
You can't do this!

91
00:04:55,716 --> 00:04:58,344
Your Padawan status
will be stripped from you,

92
00:04:58,385 --> 00:05:02,890
and you shall forfeit all rank and privileges
within the Grand Army of the Republic.

93
00:05:03,682 --> 00:05:07,061
You will be turned over
to the Republic courts to await your trial

94
00:05:07,353 --> 00:05:10,147
and whatever punishment
they will set for you.

95
00:05:10,231 --> 00:05:14,360
Henceforth, you are barred
from the Jedi Order.

96
00:05:29,917 --> 00:05:32,753
Padmé has agreed
to represent you before the Senate.

97
00:05:32,795 --> 00:05:35,756
I will do everything I can
to prove your innocence, Ahsoka.

98
00:05:35,923 --> 00:05:39,301
I am almost certain that
the person behind this is Ventress,

99
00:05:39,426 --> 00:05:41,428
and you know I wasn't working with her.

100
00:05:42,096 --> 00:05:44,807
She was at the warehouse, in the room.

101
00:05:44,932 --> 00:05:47,268
We fought, but she got away.

102
00:05:47,434 --> 00:05:49,603
Didn't any of the clones see anything?

103
00:05:51,814 --> 00:05:55,442
No, none of the clones reported
seeing Ventress at the scene.

104
00:05:55,943 --> 00:05:58,946
I thought you said Ventress left
before you went into the warehouse.

105
00:05:59,113 --> 00:06:02,992
That's what I thought, too,
but then she attacked me when I got inside.

106
00:06:03,117 --> 00:06:05,411
I'd know her red lightsabers anywhere.

107
00:06:06,453 --> 00:06:09,164
Well, if that's our only lead,
then I know what I have to do.

108
00:06:09,290 --> 00:06:12,793
Wait. Where are you going?
You can't leave now.

109
00:06:13,419 --> 00:06:15,004
Yes, I can.

110
00:06:15,129 --> 00:06:17,798
I have to find Ventress
and get to the bottom of this.

111
00:06:19,466 --> 00:06:23,137
Until we hear from Anakin,
let's work on your defense.

112
00:06:24,638 --> 00:06:26,932
Forgive me if I'm not optimistic.

113
00:06:26,974 --> 00:06:29,310
I thought I was part of that Order,

114
00:06:29,435 --> 00:06:32,646
but everyone, except Anakin,
has abandoned me.

115
00:06:32,771 --> 00:06:35,816
I'm not holding out much hope
the Senate will treat me any better.

116
00:07:15,606 --> 00:07:18,108
Anakin Skywalker.

117
00:07:18,692 --> 00:07:20,444
I know you're behind all of this.

118
00:07:20,611 --> 00:07:21,695
Prove it.

119
00:07:32,122 --> 00:07:33,791
Leave me alone!

120
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:48,222
Tell me what happened!

121
00:07:49,807 --> 00:07:52,935
When I heard your little brat
was on the run,

122
00:07:53,060 --> 00:07:55,938
I thought she might bring a large bounty.

123
00:07:56,063 --> 00:07:57,314
Bounty?

124
00:07:57,898 --> 00:08:01,986
I was going to catch your pet
and turn her over to the authorities,

125
00:08:02,069 --> 00:08:04,905
collect whatever bounty was due.

126
00:08:05,614 --> 00:08:06,657
What stopped you?

127
00:08:09,576 --> 00:08:13,455
At first, I admit,
I was just interested in the money,

128
00:08:13,580 --> 00:08:15,916
and a little bit of revenge.

129
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,251
But then I realized

130
00:08:17,334 --> 00:08:21,422
your fallen Padawan and I
had a lot in common.

131
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:24,633
How dare you compare yourself to Ahsoka?

132
00:08:24,842 --> 00:08:26,218
It's true!

133
00:08:27,386 --> 00:08:30,639
My master abandoned me,

134
00:08:30,806 --> 00:08:34,018
and that's exactly what you did to her.

135
00:08:35,602 --> 00:08:39,189
You and your precious Jedi Order.

136
00:09:33,786 --> 00:09:35,162
Ahsoka Tano,

137
00:09:36,330 --> 00:09:40,167
you have been charged with sedition
against the Jedi Order

138
00:09:40,459 --> 00:09:42,961
and the Republic itself.

139
00:09:43,295 --> 00:09:45,923
This court will decide your fate.

140
00:09:46,632 --> 00:09:49,635
Prosecution, you may begin
your arguments.

141
00:09:54,139 --> 00:09:58,685
Former Padawan Tano, I shall prove
that you were the mastermind

142
00:09:58,769 --> 00:10:01,480
behind the attack on the Jedi Temple,

143
00:10:01,563 --> 00:10:04,525
and that, once your accomplices
carried out your orders,

144
00:10:04,608 --> 00:10:06,527
you eliminated them one by one.

145
00:10:07,653 --> 00:10:09,279
When you are found guilty,

146
00:10:09,363 --> 00:10:13,033
I ask the court that the full extent
of the law be brought down upon you,

147
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:16,036
including penalty of death.

148
00:10:20,290 --> 00:10:25,462
After I left the warehouse,
after I left your little Padawan alone,

149
00:10:25,629 --> 00:10:26,964
I was walking away

150
00:10:27,131 --> 00:10:30,217
and I thought she came up behind me
to talk more,

151
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:31,593
but I was wrong.

152
00:10:31,677 --> 00:10:34,138
Someone came out of nowhere
and hit me from behind.

153
00:10:35,055 --> 00:10:37,766
Not just anyone can sneak up behind me.

154
00:10:38,183 --> 00:10:40,185
It had to be another Jedi.

155
00:10:40,352 --> 00:10:41,603
I don't believe you.

156
00:10:41,728 --> 00:10:42,980
Believe it.

157
00:10:43,188 --> 00:10:45,816
Whoever you're looking for
has my lightsabers.

158
00:10:46,066 --> 00:10:48,569
That's how you'll know
you've found the criminal.

159
00:10:48,652 --> 00:10:51,155
Well, this leads me to a dead end.

160
00:10:51,321 --> 00:10:54,158
You're the only one Ahsoka had talked to.

161
00:10:55,534 --> 00:10:56,994
That's not true.

162
00:10:57,202 --> 00:10:58,412
What do you mean?

163
00:10:59,246 --> 00:11:01,665
Your Padawan contacted the Temple.

164
00:11:01,790 --> 00:11:05,169
She spoke to someone named Barriss.

165
00:11:05,252 --> 00:11:08,547
That's why we knew to go
to the warehouse in the first place.

166
00:11:08,714 --> 00:11:12,551
It was this Barriss that told us to go there.

167
00:11:12,759 --> 00:11:15,137
If you're lying, you're dead.

168
00:11:15,512 --> 00:11:17,347
Such promises.

169
00:11:21,435 --> 00:11:22,769
Look at the facts.

170
00:11:23,187 --> 00:11:25,731
Letta Turmond called Ahsoka to her cell

171
00:11:25,814 --> 00:11:29,818
to reveal the name of the true mastermind
behind the bombing of the Jedi Temple.

172
00:11:30,027 --> 00:11:32,029
Letta told Ahsoka she was afraid.

173
00:11:32,529 --> 00:11:35,365
She told her the mastermind was a Jedi,

174
00:11:35,490 --> 00:11:37,534
and before she could reveal
the Jedi's name,

175
00:11:37,701 --> 00:11:41,371
Letta Turmond was strangled to death
by way of the Force.

176
00:11:41,997 --> 00:11:44,124
Why would Ahsoka kill Letta

177
00:11:44,208 --> 00:11:47,711
with a method that would
so obviously tie the murder to her?

178
00:11:47,961 --> 00:11:51,048
A Jedi may be responsible for the murder,

179
00:11:51,131 --> 00:11:54,051
but that Jedi is not Ahsoka Tano.

180
00:11:54,468 --> 00:11:58,639
Members of the court,
you are prosecuting the wrong Jedi.

181
00:12:01,099 --> 00:12:03,852
Well said, Senator Amidala.

182
00:12:04,144 --> 00:12:06,480
However, if she is innocent,

183
00:12:06,563 --> 00:12:11,026
then why was she seen conspiring with
known Separatist terrorist Asajj Ventress?

184
00:12:12,903 --> 00:12:15,739
Ventress set me up.
My master will prove that.

185
00:12:15,948 --> 00:12:18,033
And where is your master?

186
00:12:18,575 --> 00:12:20,953
He's trying to find the real murderer.

187
00:12:21,828 --> 00:12:24,623
Then maybe he should be looking at you!

188
00:12:48,772 --> 00:12:49,940
Enter.

189
00:12:51,358 --> 00:12:52,609
Barriss.

190
00:12:53,068 --> 00:12:54,569
I need to talk to you.

191
00:12:54,695 --> 00:12:55,904
Master Skywalker.

192
00:12:56,571 --> 00:12:57,864
How can I help you?

193
00:12:57,948 --> 00:13:01,368
I was told that you spoke with Ahsoka
before she was arrested.

194
00:13:01,785 --> 00:13:03,245
What did you say to her?

195
00:13:03,412 --> 00:13:07,457
We've been friends for a long time.
I was only trying to help her.

196
00:13:07,541 --> 00:13:08,917
I hope I'm not in any trouble.

197
00:13:09,084 --> 00:13:10,544
It's no trouble.

198
00:13:10,794 --> 00:13:12,838
I just need to know what you told her,

199
00:13:13,130 --> 00:13:14,339
and if you told anyone else.

200
00:13:14,798 --> 00:13:15,966
No.

201
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:19,261
I thought I had a clue for her,
but I really couldn't tell her anything.

202
00:13:19,803 --> 00:13:21,096
Who told you I spoke to her?

203
00:13:21,805 --> 00:13:24,141
Ventress. She told me.

204
00:13:24,683 --> 00:13:29,021
Ventress? Isn't she the one
Ahsoka says is really behind all this?

205
00:13:29,146 --> 00:13:30,564
That's what Ahsoka says,

206
00:13:30,856 --> 00:13:32,816
but I think she's wrong.

207
00:13:33,233 --> 00:13:35,360
Ventress thinks someone else is involved.

208
00:13:35,652 --> 00:13:37,195
And you believe her?

209
00:13:37,362 --> 00:13:39,531
Who else could it be, if not her?

210
00:13:39,740 --> 00:13:42,075
-Surely not Ahsoka.
-No.

211
00:13:42,784 --> 00:13:44,494
I don't think it was Ahsoka, either.

212
00:13:45,329 --> 00:13:48,832
I think both Ahsoka and Ventress
are telling the truth.

213
00:13:48,999 --> 00:13:51,877
But there's only one way to find out.

214
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:56,006
Funny, those belong to Ventress.

215
00:13:59,843 --> 00:14:01,094
You should've gotten rid of them.

216
00:14:01,261 --> 00:14:02,554
I think they suit me.

217
00:14:04,056 --> 00:14:05,098
Ah!

218
00:14:07,559 --> 00:14:13,273
I'm sure many of you
look at this former Jedi and think,

219
00:14:13,357 --> 00:14:18,737
"Surely she cannot be this murderer
or saboteur that they speak of."

220
00:14:18,862 --> 00:14:23,867
And yet, think of all the times
we have been fooled by the Separatists,

221
00:14:24,034 --> 00:14:26,161
and how they have infiltrated
the Republic,

222
00:14:26,328 --> 00:14:32,501
and ask yourself,
"Is this yet another Separatist scheme,

223
00:14:33,502 --> 00:14:40,384
"another way to rip the Jedi,
and subsequently all of us, apart?"

224
00:14:45,263 --> 00:14:48,100
Ahsoka trusted you and you betrayed her.

225
00:14:48,558 --> 00:14:50,394
I've learned that trust is overrated.

226
00:14:50,477 --> 00:14:53,647
The only thing the Jedi Council believes in
is violence.

227
00:15:12,290 --> 00:15:13,792
Cease hostilities!

228
00:15:20,757 --> 00:15:21,842
Barriss!

229
00:15:40,527 --> 00:15:41,570
Look out!

230
00:16:23,487 --> 00:16:26,656
The members of the court
have reached a decision.

231
00:16:36,833 --> 00:16:38,835
Ahsoka Tano,

232
00:16:39,377 --> 00:16:42,339
-by an overwhelming count of...
-Chancellor!

233
00:16:44,424 --> 00:16:51,097
I hope you have a reason for bursting
into our proceedings, Master Skywalker.

234
00:16:51,681 --> 00:16:56,394
I'm here with evidence and a confession
from the person responsible

235
00:16:56,478 --> 00:16:59,314
for all the crimes
Ahsoka has been accused of,

236
00:16:59,606 --> 00:17:01,107
Barriss Of fee,

237
00:17:01,441 --> 00:17:03,485
member of the Jedi Order

238
00:17:03,777 --> 00:17:05,028
and traitor.

239
00:17:11,201 --> 00:17:13,370
Barriss, is that true?

240
00:17:13,954 --> 00:17:15,539
Tell them the truth.

241
00:17:20,627 --> 00:17:22,003
I did it,

242
00:17:22,170 --> 00:17:24,130
because I've come to realize

243
00:17:24,214 --> 00:17:26,967
what many people in the Republic
have come to realize,

244
00:17:27,050 --> 00:17:29,844
that the Jedi are the ones
responsible for this war,

245
00:17:30,011 --> 00:17:34,057
that we've so lost our way
that we've become villains in this conflict,

246
00:17:34,558 --> 00:17:36,518
that we are the ones
that should be put on trial,

247
00:17:36,685 --> 00:17:38,061
all of us!

248
00:17:39,062 --> 00:17:43,567
And my attack on the Temple was
an attack on what the Jedi have become,

249
00:17:44,067 --> 00:17:46,570
an army fighting for the dark side,

250
00:17:46,653 --> 00:17:49,489
fallen from the light
that we once held so dear.

251
00:17:49,573 --> 00:17:51,908
This Republic is failing!

252
00:17:52,742 --> 00:17:54,828
It's only a matter of time.

253
00:17:57,872 --> 00:17:59,541
Take her away.

254
00:18:23,023 --> 00:18:27,068
Ahsoka, I am so sorry,

255
00:18:28,236 --> 00:18:29,863
about everything.

256
00:18:31,906 --> 00:18:35,827
You have our most humble apologies,
little Ahsoka.

257
00:18:36,328 --> 00:18:39,205
The Council was wrong to accuse you.

258
00:18:39,331 --> 00:18:42,834
You have shown
such great strength and resilience

259
00:18:42,917 --> 00:18:46,046
in your struggle to prove your innocence.

260
00:18:46,546 --> 00:18:49,257
This is the true sign of a Jedi Knight.

261
00:18:49,674 --> 00:18:54,179
This was actually your great trial.
Now we see that.

262
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:57,182
We understand that the Force works
in mysterious ways,

263
00:18:57,515 --> 00:18:59,100
and, because of this trial,

264
00:18:59,225 --> 00:19:02,687
you have become a greater Jedi
than you would have otherwise.

265
00:19:03,897 --> 00:19:07,359
Back into the Order you may come.

266
00:19:09,736 --> 00:19:11,738
They're asking you back, Ahsoka.

267
00:19:14,866 --> 00:19:16,826
I'm asking you back.

268
00:19:45,438 --> 00:19:46,940
I'm sorry, Master,

269
00:19:47,899 --> 00:19:49,693
but I'm not coming back.

270
00:20:22,142 --> 00:20:23,643
Ahsoka! Wait!

271
00:20:25,437 --> 00:20:27,647
Ahsoka, I need to talk to you!

272
00:20:33,361 --> 00:20:36,156
Why are you doing this?

273
00:20:36,322 --> 00:20:38,450
The Council didn't trust me,

274
00:20:38,575 --> 00:20:40,660
so how can I trust myself?

275
00:20:40,952 --> 00:20:42,454
What about me?

276
00:20:42,579 --> 00:20:44,998
I believed in you. I stood by you!

277
00:20:45,790 --> 00:20:48,209
I know you believe in me, Anakin,

278
00:20:48,293 --> 00:20:50,295
and I'm grateful for that.

279
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:52,547
But this isn't about you.

280
00:20:52,630 --> 00:20:55,175
I can't stay here any longer,

281
00:20:55,717 --> 00:20:56,801
not now.

282
00:20:57,927 --> 00:21:02,557
The Jedi Order is your life.
You can't just throw it away like this!

283
00:21:02,724 --> 00:21:05,393
Ahsoka, you are making a mistake.

284
00:21:05,769 --> 00:21:06,895
Maybe.

285
00:21:07,479 --> 00:21:09,606
But I have to sort this out on my own,

286
00:21:10,148 --> 00:21:11,691
without the Council

287
00:21:12,650 --> 00:21:14,152
and without you.

288
00:21:16,821 --> 00:21:19,699
I understand. More than you realize,

289
00:21:20,575 --> 00:21:24,788
I understand wanting
to walk away from the Order.

290
00:21:26,956 --> 00:21:28,249
I know.

291
00:21:28,273 --> 00:21:33,273
http://hiqve.com/

